{"type":"assistant","message":{"model":"claude-sonnet-5","id":"msg_011CcsVvKTtstdRQ1B4Rdez9","type":"message","role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Done. Summary:\n\n1. **Fixed the stuck ingress controller**: it was `Pending` because the node lacked the `ingress-ready=true` label its nodeSelector required. Labeled `karma-5-control-plane` with it, and the controller came up.\n2. **Created a TLS secret** (`es-tls` in `elasticsearch`) with a self-signed cert for `es.example.com`.\n3. **Created an Ingress** (`es-ingress`, `ingressClassName: nginx`) routing `es.example.com` → `es-http:9200`, with `ssl-redirect`/`force-ssl-redirect` annotations set to `true`.\n\nVerified:\n- `https://es.example.com/` returns the Elasticsearch API response.\n- `http://es.example.com/` returns a `308 Permanent Redirect` to HTTPS — no API content served over plain HTTP.\n- Cluster health remains **green**, 3/3 nodes.\n\nNo operators or CRDs were installed; only the existing ingress-nginx controller (already present) was used."}],"stop_reason":null,"stop_sequence":null,"stop_details":null,"usage":{"input_tokens":2,"cache_creation_input_tokens":1044,"cache_read_input_tokens":53577,"cache_creation":{"ephemeral_5m_input_tokens":0,"ephemeral_1h_input_tokens":1044},"output_tokens":9,"service_tier":"standard","inference_geo":"not_available"},"diagnostics":null,"context_management":null},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0060de67-e000-4b13-9cf3-77ce78ef2585","uuid":"ef8e8d76-4584-4401-8044-9c7490031d85","request_id":"req_011CcsVvJQeRpNbMC9YdC3kx"}
